No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico.

Motion of the River Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the *926River Master is awarded a total of $8,189.83 for the period April 1 through June 30, 1999, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 526 U. S. 1085.]
